-- Cincinnati Beats Top-Seeded Syracuse 71-68 in Big East Semifinal
-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 2012-03-10T02:13:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-10/cincinnati-beats-top-seeded-syracuse-71-68-in-big-east-semifinal.html
The University of Cincinnati
defeated top-seeded Syracuse University 71-68 in the semifinals
of the Big East mens’s basketball tournament.  The fourth-seeded Bearcats fought off a second-half rally
by the Orange, who were down by 12 at the half, at Madison
Square Garden in  New York .  Cincinnati will play the winner of tonight’s game between
 Notre Dame  and Louisville in tomorrow’s championship contest.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  